videos.description: Adam Miller cuts to the basket, avoids the block and gets the shot to fall, putting Illinois on the board.
videos.headline: Miller drains circus shot

videos.description: Illinois freshman Andre Curbelo grabs the rebound and speeds down the court for a reverse layup.
